{"tid":1306942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「智慧燈柱」，試著說「監控燈柱」","createTime":"2019-07-11T10:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:13:52.000Z","uid":252321,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c78ac87fcd7aeff198e3febee705fc19f04fd50c","tid":1306942,"uid":252321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打開過，點知大家都仲係講智能燈柱/智慧燈柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少reframe用詞嘅重要性，「反送中」頭兩次遊行都係分別得1萬同10萬人出嚟，唔信自己，因為當初係用「反對修訂逃犯條例」咁又長又累贅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，「監控燈柱」同「社會信用評分制度」係掛鈎的，我哋都要reframe後者，例如「大型監控計劃」/「滅聲監控」/「圈養滅聲監控」，我哋都要spread開呢個信息，不過可以遲啲要再帶風向，因為同時需要媒體 &amp; 泛民配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之，現階段，文宣/整圖巴打要緊記：<br />\n不要說「智慧燈柱」，試著說「監控燈柱」<br />\n不要說「智慧燈柱」，試著說「監控燈柱」<br />\n不要說「智慧燈柱」，試著說「監控燈柱」"},{"pid":"11e2bc1f818cfd0e4b949f44b81cb34042288068","tid":1306942,"uid":258696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852xdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=c54e41fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852xdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=0576faff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 6.12一周月行動 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10